
Step 1
aptitude install odbcinst

Step 2
Download connector at
https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/odbc/

Step 3
Edit /etc/odbcinst.ini and add:
[MySQL]
Description = ODBC for MySQL
Driver = /home/oidplus/public_html/oidplus_dev/test/mysql-connector-odbc-8.0.17-linux-debian9-x86-64bit/lib/libmyodbc8a.so
Setup = /home/oidplus/public_html/oidplus_dev/test/mysql-connector-odbc-8.0.17-linux-debian9-x86-64bit/lib/libmyodbc8S.so
FileUsage = 1

